---
import Page from "@layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Page path={Astro.url.pathname} title="Privacy Policy">
	<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
	<p>Last updated: <time datetime="2025-09-06">September 6th, 2025</time></p>

	<h3>Data Collection and Use</h2>
	<p>We store hashed IP addresses and hardware IDs (HWIDs) to ensure the security of our service. This includes authentication, preventing abuse, and enforcing bans. We do not process or share your personal data beyond what is necessary for security purposes. All data handling is based on our <i>legitimate interest</i> <a href="https://gdpr-info.eu/art-6-gdpr/" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" target="_blank">(Article 6(1)(f) GDPR)</a> in maintaining the safety of our service.</p>

	<h3>Retention</h3>
	<p>We retain this data only as long as necessary to fulfill these purposes.</p>

	<h3>User Rights</h3>
	<p>
		You may request access to or deletion of your data. Please note:
		<ul>
			<li>If you are blacklisted, deletion may not be possible depending on the severity of the situation.</li>
			<li>If you have premium access, requesting deletion will automatically revoke your premium access.</li>
		</ul>
		To make a request, contact us on our Discord.
	</p>
</Page>
